%% x-story-finalizer: Story Finalizer Task Creator
%% Creates final Story task after manual testing passes (invoked by x-story-reviewer Pass 1)
%% Generates comprehensive task with 11 sections: E2E-first Risk-Based Testing (Priority ≥15)
%% Excludes performance/load testing - see references/risk_based_testing_guide.md

graph TD
    Start([Start: Create Story Finalizer Task<br/>Invoked by x-story-reviewer Pass 1]) --> Phase1[Phase 1: Discovery<br/>Team ID + Parent Story]

    Phase1 --> Phase2[Phase 2: Load Manual Test Results<br/>Parse Linear comment Format v1.0<br/>AC + Test Results + Edge Cases + Errors + Integration]

    Phase2 --> Phase3[Phase 3: Story + Tasks Analysis<br/>Study Project Test Files<br/>Analyze Story + all Done impl tasks]

    Phase3 --> Phase4[Phase 4: Risk-Based Test Planning]

    subgraph RiskPlanning [Risk-Based Testing]
        Risk1[Step 1: Risk Assessment<br/>Priority = Business Impact × Probability]
        Risk1 --> Risk2[Step 2: E2E Test Selection<br/>2-5 tests Priority ≥15]
        Risk2 --> Risk3[Step 3: Unit Test Selection<br/>5-15 tests Priority ≥15]
        Risk3 --> Risk4[Step 4: Integration Test Selection<br/>3-8 tests Priority ≥15]
        Risk4 --> Risk5[Step 5: Validation<br/>10-28 total no duplication]
    end

    Phase4 --> Risk1
    Risk5 --> Phase5

    Phase5[Phase 5: Impact Analysis]

    subgraph Impact [4 Impact Areas]
        Impact1[Existing Tests to Fix/Update]
        Impact2[Infrastructure Changes<br/>package.json Docker configs]
        Impact3[Documentation Updates<br/>README tests/README CHANGELOG]
        Impact4[Legacy Code Cleanup<br/>workarounds backward compat deprecated]
    end

    Phase5 --> Impact1
    Impact1 --> Impact2
    Impact2 --> Impact3
    Impact3 --> Impact4
    Impact4 --> Phase6

    Phase6[Phase 6: Generate Complete Story Finalizer Task<br/>11 sections: Context Risk Matrix E2E Integration Unit<br/>Coverage DoD Existing Tests Infra Docs Cleanup]

    Phase6 --> Confirm{User confirms?}
    Confirm -->|Yes| Create[Phase 7: Create Linear Issue<br/>as Story's final task]
    Confirm -->|No| Phase6
    Create --> End([End])

    %% Styling
    classDef discovery fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:2px
    classDef analysis fill:#FFF9C4,stroke:#F57C00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decision fill:#FFE0B2,stroke:#E64A19,stroke-width:2px
    classDef action fill:#C8E6C9,stroke:#388E3C,stroke-width:2px

    class Phase1,Phase2,Phase3 discovery
    class Phase4,Risk1,Risk2,Risk3,Risk4,Risk5,Phase5,Impact1,Impact2,Impact3,Impact4,Phase6 analysis
    class Confirm decision
    class Create action
